description: City: Walla Walla, WAAndrae's Kitchen is Walla Walla's first gourmet food truck! We are located in front of The Marcus Whitman Hotel on 2nd Ave in Walla Walla for Lunch Monday-Friday from 11-2:30. We can be found out at various wineries on the weekends. AK's is a fully self contained mobile commercial kitchen that can come to you! We can do any of the following:- Vineyard Dinners- Winery Events- Wedding Receptions and Rehearsal Dinners- Corporate Functions- Private events- Anything you can think of!Chef Andrae Bopp is classically trained and can prepare any type of menu to suit your needs. From classic comfort food, to high end plated dinners and everything in between. If you can think of it, we can make it happen. Contact us and let us make your next event, the one that everyone talks about!
name: Andrae's Kitchen
